<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">春启新程，教苑焕新。为筑牢教学质量根基，抓实教风学风建设，引导师生迅速投入新学期教学生活，3月5日，校、院领导深入教学一线，共同走进课堂与师生同上“开学第一课”，实地督查教学运行情况，为新学期教学工作开好局、起好步保驾护航。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264233390.jpg" alt="1774264233390.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264233390.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264257300.jpg" alt="1774264257300.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264257300.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264279840.jpg" alt="1774264279840.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264279840.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">此次校领导深入经管课堂听课，是学校抓实教学质量监管、压实教学管理职责的务实行动，也为学院凝练优良教风学风、推进经管专业教学创新明晰了方向。我院师生精神风貌积极向上，教学秩序规范有序。学生出勤整齐、专注度高，主动参与课堂互动，课堂氛围浓厚热烈。各班级教学组织有序开展，教学设备运转正常，全方位保障了新学期教学工作平稳开局。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264298298.jpg" alt="1774264298298.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264298298.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264318130.jpg" alt="1774264318130.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1774264318130.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">征程新启，经管学子将以奋斗为笔，笃行不怠、聚力成长。经济管理学院也将持续强化教学督导检查，将教学巡查作为抓实学风教风建设的重要抓手，全力提升课堂教学质量，助力育人工作提质增效。</span></p>